SHE WAS THIRTY-ONE YEARS OLD AND

14:22.195 --> 14:23.396
A MOTHER OF TWO, A HIGH-SCHOOL

14:23.396 --> 14:24.697
CHEMISTRY TEACHER AND BASKETBALL

14:24.697 --> 14:27.300
COACH IN OXFORD, OHIO.

14:27.300 --> 14:28.568
SHE WAS ON HER WAY TO A TEACHER-

14:28.568 --> 14:29.836
TRAINING WORKSHOP ON A SATURDAY

14:29.836 --> 14:31.204
MORNING WHEN HER LIGHT TURNED

14:31.204 --> 14:33.072
GREEN.

