SO EVEN WHEN POLICE AREN'T

14:54.160 --> 14:55.428
THERE, DRIVERS THINK TWICE

14:55.428 --> 14:57.196
BEFORE RUNNING A LIGHT.

14:57.196 --> 14:58.664
AND THE PROOF THAT THEY WORK,

14:58.664 --> 14:59.999
ACCORDING TO THE OBERHAUSERS, IS

14:59.999 --> 15:01.501
A FORTY-MINUTE DRIVE FROM THEIR

15:01.501 --> 15:02.835
FARMHOUSE IN OHIO'S STATE

15:02.835 --> 15:05.238
CAPITAL.

