AND AT LOCATIONS WITH CAMERAS,

15:17.350 --> 15:18.985
RIGHT-ANGLE CRASHES FELL 74%

15:18.985 --> 15:24.924
BETWEEN 2005 AND 2008.

15:24.924 --> 15:27.226
>> WE HAVE SIGNIFICANTLY ALTERED

15:27.226 --> 15:29.529
DRIVER BEHAVIOR FOR THE GOOD

15:29.529 --> 15:30.363
HERE IN COLUMBUS, OHIO.

15:30.363 --> 15:31.531
>> Reporter: GEORGE SPEAKS IS

15:31.531 --> 15:32.932
THE CITY'S PUBLIC SAFETY

