AND SENDS THAT INFORMATION BACK

16:19.245 --> 16:20.513
TO THE COLUMBUS POLICE

16:20.513 --> 16:21.547
DEPARTMENT.

16:21.547 --> 16:23.149
THERE, COPS LIKE LIEUTENANT

16:23.149 --> 16:25.184
BRENT MULL REVIEW THE EVIDENCE.

